protective_factors: Strong inhibitor: Explicit concern for family ('I couldn't do that to them')
Willingness to comply with treatment changes
risk_factors: Presence of passive suicidal ideation (wish to disappear)
Significant depressive symptom burden (sleep disturbance, anhedonia, weight loss, guilt)
Sub-optimal response to initial antidepressant dose (*Sertraline* 50mg)
clinical_actions: Follow-up scheduled for medication efficacy and side effects
